HEADWORD: Transforate
<hw>Trans"fo*rate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>transforatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>transforare</ets> to pierce
through; <ets>trans</ets> through + <ets>forare</ets> to bore.]</ety>
<def>To bore through; to perforate.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

